        "subject": "LU-5781 ldlm: call LRU policy and set PENDING flag atomically",
        "message": "LU-5781 ldlm: call LRU policy and set PENDING flag atomically\n\notherwise, lock can be re-used in between and dirty pages added\nunder it. cancel of such a lock requires a data flush, what results\nin a deadlock for lock replay case.\n\nSigned-off-by: Vitaly Fertman <vitaly_fertman@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: I60d2a8827baf399c294c6db9699aff9e7b6e3033\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-2176\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
